  "text": "Combining the result above with the discussion in Section 2.2 about the two types of edges in the directed graph G d , we have the complete answer for Open Question 1 of [CITATION_1] : the necessary and sufficient conditions on the edge {e} → {e 1 , e 2 } or the edge {e} → {e 1 , e 2 , e 3 } in G",
